title: End Game Screen Bug

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: hey guys just finish a game I found this thing weird I got the last game screen shot instead of the new game{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}

replies.body:
Could you elaborate on what you mean but you got this instead of the new game please? There doesn't appear to be anything wrong in the screenshot itself, but it seems you are saying you saw this when you should have been seeing something else?

It's a little unclear what you mean/what the problem is here. :)
hey if you look at the top right and the score board there is the difference.
Agreed, I see nothing out of the ordinary in your screenshot.
